dentità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\" src=\"ISic000706_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000706.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\" src=\"ISic000706-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000706_leftthreequarter_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\" src=\"ISic000706_leftthreequarter_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000706_leftthreequarter.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\" src=\"ISic000706_leftthreequarter-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000706_rightthreequarter_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\" src=\"ISic000706_rightthreequarter_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000706_rightthreequarter.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\" src=\"ISic000706_rightthreequarter-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000706_top_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\" src=\"ISic000706_top_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000706_top.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\" src=\"ISic000706_top-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text checked by Prag against photograph\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-9859-2494\">Tom Gavin\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Sacred to the shades of the underworld. To Lucius Arrius Herma; he lived 5 months, 25 days. Charito made (this) for his well-deserving home-born slave.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2354-4452\">Estella Kessler\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Den Seelen der Unterwelt gewidmet. Für Lucius Arrius Herma; er lebte für 5 Monate, 25 Tage. Charito hat (dies) gemacht für seinen verdienstvollen Sklaven.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>As Manganaro notes, it seems a little unusual that the deceased infant, a slave, is recorded with the full tria nomina, while the owner, Charito, is not (but presumably was Lucius Arrius Charito).\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 1989.0341i \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1989 171 no.39 fig.43 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 58 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscr