0706_rightthreequarter.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\" src=\"ISic000706_rightthreequarter-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000706_top_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\" src=\"ISic000706_top_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000706_top.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\" src=\"ISic000706_top-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":247,"html":248},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text checked by Prag against photograph\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":250,"html":251},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-9859-2494\">Tom Gavin\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Sacred to the shades of the underworld. To Lucius Arrius Herma; he lived 5 months, 25 days. Charito made (this) for his well-deserving home-born slave.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":250,"html":253},"\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2354-4452\">Estella Kessler\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Den Seelen der Unterwelt gewidmet. Für Lucius Arrius Herma; er lebte für 5 Monate, 25 Tage. Charito hat (dies) gemacht für seinen verdienstvollen Sklaven.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":255,"html":256},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>As Manganaro notes, it seems a little unusual that the deceased infant, a slave, is recorded with the full tria nomina, while the owner, Charito, is not (but presumably was Lucius Arrius Charito).\u003C/p>  ",{"id":258,"html":259},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 1989.0341i \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1989 171 no.39 fig.43 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 58 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":261,"html":262},"handnote","\u003Cp> Line 1-10  15-22  Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/p>",{"id":264,"html":265},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[267,269,272,273],{"html":268},"Text encoding: Tom Gavin, Jonathan Prag",{"id":270,"lang":138,"html":271},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>d(is) · m(anibus) · s(acrum) \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Lucio ·  Arrio\n                    Herme\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Lucio\">L(ucio)\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Arrio\">Arrio\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Herme\">Herme\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>vixit \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u00