f the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic000706_leftthreequarter_tiled.tif\" height=\"3456px\" width=\"5184px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000706_leftthreequarter.jpg\" height=\"3456px\" width=\"5184px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic000706_rightthreequarter_tiled.tif\" height=\"3456px\" width=\"5184px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000706_rightthreequarter.jpg\" height=\"3456px\" width=\"5184px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"top\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic000706_top_tiled.tif\" height=\"3456px\" width=\"5184px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000706_top.jpg\" height=\"3456px\" width=\"5184px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro, 2018\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n        \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#TG #JP\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>d\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>is\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g>  \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>m\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>anibus\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g>  \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>s\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>acrum\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>L\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ucio\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/name> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g>  \u003Cname>Arrio\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>\u003Cname>Herme\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>vixit\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\"/>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>mens\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>es\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g>  \u003Cnum value=\"5\">\u003Chi rend=\"supraline\">V\u003C/hi>\u003C/num>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"6\"/>dies \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g>  \u003Cnum value=\"25\">XX\u003Chi rend=\"small\">V\u003C/hi>\u003C/num>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"7\"/>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>f\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ecit\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>b\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ene\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g>  \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>m\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>erenti\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \n                    \u003Clb n=\"8\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>Chari                    \n                    \u003Clb n=\"9\" break=\"no\"/>to\u003C/name>\u003C/persName> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g>  ver\n                    \u003Clb n=\"10\" break=\"no\"/>nae suo\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>Text checked by Prag against photograph\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#TG\">\n                \u003Cp>Sacred to the shades of the underworld. To Lucius Arrius Herma; he lived 5 months, 25 days. Charito made (this) for his well-deserving home-born slave.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"de\" resp=\"#EK\">\n                \u003Cp>Den Seelen der Unterwelt gewidmet. Für Lucius Arrius Herma; er lebte für 5 Monate, 25 Tage. Charito hat (dies) gemacht für seinen verdienstvollen Sklaven.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>As Manganaro notes, it seems a little unusual that the deceased infant, a slave, is recorded with the full tria nomina, while the owner, Charito, is not (but presumably was Lucius Arrius Charito).\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"AE\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>1989.0341i\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/R46KDTZX\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Manganaro\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1989\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>171 no.39 fig.43\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/EZMBJ6GN\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IMusCatania\">\n                         \u003Cauthor>Korhonen\u003C/author>\n                         \u003Cdate>2004\u003C/date> \n                        \u003CcitedRange>58\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/2EUC82DH\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl/>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
